/www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/Th%E1%BB%8B-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%B1-th%E1%BB%ABa-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-hi%E1%BB%87u-kh%C3%A1m/poem-ViMdvZId4AXkLsPGdsDjPg">Thị Trương tự thừa, Vương hiệu khám - 示張寺丞王校勘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/author-vOEpptlMHWVC0_k_NsTzRg">Án Thù</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/T%E1%BB%A9c-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Nh%E1%BA%A5t-tu%E1%BA%BF-l%C3%A2m-hoa-t%E1%BB%A9c-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%C6%B0u/poem-2Y9kqT5s8QlUNT6hoWL7fA">Tức nhật (Nhất tuế lâm hoa tức nhật hưu) - 即日（一歲林花即日休）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0-nhi-l%E1%BB%87nh/poem-F67e3sctiLeRZE1fqyZs-w">Tương tư nhi lệnh - 相思兒令</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/author-vOEpptlMHWVC0_k_NsTzRg">Án Thù</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-L%C3%BD/U%E1%BB%B7-gia-n%E1%BB%99i/poem-1Wai90NIRez-REzjhCaucg">Uỷ gia nội - 慰家內</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-L%C3%BD/author-25FyZ6rpi0e-evNzYaWVZQ">Nguyễn Văn Lý</a>)<br></div>	</div>
